## DioxusDemoMessage

dioxus_demo_message-Body = A standalone 49/61-key MPE polyphonic synthesizer where pressure, pitch, and gesture shape each note under your fingers.
dioxus_demo_message-PanelLabel = Expressive E Osmose
dioxus_demo_message-ResourceBody = The EaganMatrix engine by Haken Audio turns expressive gestures into analog, physical-modeling, and hybrid timbres.
dioxus_demo_message-ResourceTitle = EaganMatrix engine
dioxus_demo_message-ResultBody = The Augmented Keyboard Action captures pressure, high-resolution aftertouch, and lateral motion for per-note bends and vibrato.
dioxus_demo_message-ResultLabel = Gesture-sensitive keybed
dioxus_demo_message-RuntimeBody = MPE-ready expression lets slides, vibrato, pressure swells, and articulations stay independent across the performance.
